linesOfText.text: What do bees do if they want to use public transport?
Wait at the buzz stop!
What is a French cat’s favorite pudding?
Chocolate mousse!
What is a bear’s favorite drink?
Koka-Koala

What is worse than
raining cats and dogs?
Raining elephants!
How did the toad die?
He simply croaked.
How are tigers like sergeants in the army?
They both wear stripes!
What is smarter than a talking cat?
A spelling bee!
Where do birds invest their money?
In the stork market!
Why is an elephant braver than a hen?
Because the elephant isn’t chicken.
Why do dogs run in circles?
Because it’s hard to run in squares!
What did the baby elephant get when the daddy elephant sneezed?
Out of the way!
What do you get if you cross a parrot with a woodpecker?
A bird that talks in Morse code!
What kind of birds do you usually find locked up?
Jail birds!
What did the hungry Dalmatian say when he had a meal?
That hit the spots!
How do you stop an angry elephant from charging?
Take away its credit cards!
How long do chickens work?
Around the cluck!
What is a dog’s favorite flower?
Anything in your garden!
How does a lion greet the other animals in the field?
Pleased to eat you!
How did the little Scottish dog feel when he saw a monster?
Terrier-fied!
What is a cat’s favorite TV show?
The evening mews!
What birds spend all their time on their knees?
Birds of prey?

What happens when it rains
cats and dogs?
You can step in a poodle!
What did the bus driver say to the frog?
Hop on!
Why did the snowman call his dog Frost?
Because Frost bites!
What do you call a crazy chicken?
A cuckoo cluck!
What did the clean dog say to the insect?
Long time no fleas!
